[[File:Kiev Kreschatik after liberation November 1943.jpg|thumb|right|Kiev's [[Khreshchatyk|Khreshchatyk Street]] after the liberation of Kiev.]] The '''70th Anniversary of the Liberation of Kiev''' was a celebration in [[Kiev]], [[Ukraine]], on November 6, 2013, on the occasion of the 70th anniversary of the liberation of Kiev from the Nazi Invaders.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ntv.ru/novosti/amp/708798|title=Украина отмечает 70-летие освобождения Киева от фашистских захватчиков // НТВ.Ru|publisher=www.ntv.ru|language=ru|access-date=2017-12-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://racurs.ua/news-17857-v-kieve-proshel-voennyy-parad-foto|title=В Киеве прошел военный парад (ФОТО)|access-date=2017-12-04|language=ru}}</ref>
== Events == Kiev hosted a military parade in honor of the 70th anniversary of the liberation of Kiev on Khreschatyk Street.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ukrinform.ru/amp/rubric-other_news/1572127-po_kreshchatiku_proehalis_rariteti_voyni_fotoreportag_1574512.html|title=По Крещатику проехались раритеты войны. Фоторепортаж - 06.11.2013 17:30 — Новости Укринформ|publisher=www.ukrinform.ru|access-date=2017-12-04}}</ref> several dozens of military equipment passed, including the T-34 tank and the famous "Katyusha".<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://fakty.ictv.ua/ru/videos/48365/|title=Парад в Киеве: по Крещатику проехались танки и раздались выстрелы |date=2013-11-06|work=ФАКТИ|access-date=2017-12-03}}</ref> In addition, after this, a procession of military bands took place which included the [[Military Music Department of the General Staff of the Ukrainian Armed Forces]], the Military Orchestra of the National Defense University, and the military band of the interior ministry, also with the participation of the honor guard of the interior ministry.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://racurs.ua/news-17857-v-kieve-proshel-voennyy-parad-foto|title=В Киеве прошел военный парад |access-date=2017-10-29|language=ru}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://lb.ua/society/2013/11/06/238872_osvobozhdenie.html|title=В Киеве прошли мероприятия, посвященные 70-летию освобождения Киева|publisher=LB.ua|access-date=2017-12-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://photo.ukrinform.ua/rus/current/photo.php?id=577108|title=В столице устроили грандиозный военный парад|publisher=photo.ukrinform.ua|access-date=2017-12-04}}</ref>
After the parade, solemn events were held in the park of Eternal Glory, where veterans, representatives of the public and labor collectives, students of schools and universities honored the memory of those who died in the battle of Kiev.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://rg.ru/amp/2013/11/06/kiev-site-anons.html|title=В Киеве прошел парад в честь годовщины освобождения города от фашистов |work=Российская газета |language=ru|access-date=2017-12-04}}</ref>
In the evening, a concert was organized on Maydan Nezalezhnosti, which ended with a festive fireworks display.
