{{Infobox motorsport championship | logo = | pixels = | caption = | category = | country/region = [[Slovakia]] | inaugural2 = 1994 | folded = | drivers = | teams = | tyres = | champion driver = {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Pavel Valoušek]] | manufacturer = | current_season = | website = [http://hu.rallye.sk/en/ rallye.sk] }}
The '''Slovak Rally Championship''' is a [[rallying]] series based in the [[Slovakia]]. The first championship was run in 1994.
